{"tid":533221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(多對話圖)到底有幾多借’偽術’搞model嘅攝影師？","createTime":"2018-01-18T14:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T05:49:15.000Z","uid":163582,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"68e861bb964789b10450c7767f29110f5e188d46","tid":533221,"uid":163582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T14:21:37.000Z","msg":"**我所有ac嘅bio已經寫明左，不接受任何有色情成份暴露或者非公眾場所嘅約拍**<br />\n<br />\n呢個所謂影「藝術相」嘅攝影師其實好似已經搵左我三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一次冇明確咁樣講佢係想影呢種相，好似只問我可唔可以約拍<br />\n<br />\n第二次問我可唔可以影性感，我話唔可以<br />\n<br />\n第三次去我另外一個ac問，我同佢講話你已經dm過我，我話唔影嗰啲類型嘅相，跟住佢話唔影性感、咸相可以影其他不過人工低啲，呢啲就係我同佢嘅對話。<br />\n<br />\n喺圖入邊可以睇到佢根本借藝術黎揾女影咸相。你話呢個人到底影相為乜野。之後問我idea係點樣，其實我已經知道佢想點，跟住我咪答佢，佢最尾又係都返轉頭叫我除晒衫學返自己個idea俾佢畫🤣聊我影呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好人好姐，無啦啦做咩叫啲Model除衫佢影呢啲野？<br />\n仲要係咁同我拗咩係藝術<br />\n仲要叫model影嗰啲咁樣除晒裙又掀裙相(即係意思話人工低啲嗰隻呀🤣🤣🤣<br />\n目的會唔會太明顯<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/18/221945_0024ab562af8d7116301dce088a31c9e.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F18%2F221945_0024ab562af8d7116301dce088a31c9e.jpeg&h=ad760ab1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/18/221948_3832e72d7a617a345079956a115ac955.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F18%2F221948_3832e72d7a617a345079956a115ac955.png&h=3d6cc477&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/18/221949_4fb425d0d11ad462800478f2842424fe.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F18%2F221949_4fb425d0d11ad462800478f2842424fe.jpeg&h=77fad842&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/18/221956_2dfe6d8eb3e984488a440ffe417a813a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%